{"tid":2510315,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被迫寫賀錦麗送書假報道 記者劈炮","createTime":"2021-04-30T05:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:42:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13ac2e867457dbd5a07f14183698f04b30d2ad50","tid":2510315,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/JCLVGD6IBRCIJOVSTVHRIE2F3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FJCLVGD6IBRCIJOVSTVHRIE2F3Y%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT97g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=b6fd855c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FJCLVGD6IBRCIJOVSTVHRIE2F3Y%2F&h=04252207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/JCLVGD6IBRCIJOVSTVHRIE2F3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n被迫寫賀錦麗送書假報道 記者劈炮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3kjL74rSnKlT3owwh_44IokgYcw=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LSCE6UNXOZCXPLDMK7O237P77A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3kjL74rSnKlT3owwh_44IokgYcw%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLSCE6UNXOZCXPLDMK7O237P77A.jpg&h=0624d89d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■難民中心出現賀錦麗童書《超級英雄無處不在》引起風波。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約郵報》上周報道，加州長灘難民中心的小人蛇迎新禮物中，包括由負責處理難民問題的副總統賀錦麗撰寫、前年出版的兒童讀物。報道被揭發有誤後，報章抽起報道改寫再「出街」。負責記者前日宣佈辭職，聲稱被迫撰寫錯誤報道而無法拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賀被指藉難民問題謀利益<br />\n<br />\n報道上周五「出街」後在保守派政圈及媒體廣泛流傳，引起對賀錦麗在難民問題上謀取個人利益的質疑。長灘難民中心發言人證實，有社區人士在捐書活動捐贈了一本出自賀錦麗的兒童讀物《超級英雄無處不在》，強調只將收到的贈書放在中心書架，中心事前無揀選、聯邦及市政府亦無購買該書作為小人蛇迎新禮物。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》前日在網站大幅修改報道再「出街」，刪除該書是迎新禮物的說法，補充是由社區人士捐贈，但仍然聲稱該書在難民中心，是展示拜登政府張臂歡迎難民的姿態。<br />\n<br />\n負責撰寫報道的記者伊塔利亞諾（Laura Italiano）前日宣佈已辭職，稱導火線是有人下令她撰寫錯誤報道，她無法堅決反對。《紐約郵報》將傳媒跟進問題轉交公關，未有回應指控。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ggQFW-4J3c_Vs8RUIDUHiCHyuyY=/510x532/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VQ3QPVU6N5AFNMUGRHZ4KLFM5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FggQFW-4J3c_Vs8RUIDUHiCHyuyY%3D%2F510x532%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVQ3QPVU6N5AFNMUGRHZ4KLFM5I.jpg&h=6b505f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊塔利亞諾"},{"pid":"5c3f3293423766e2df8f84f66d87aa46fec0f627","tid":2510315,"uid":25240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報道被揭發有誤後，報章抽起報道改寫再「出街」。負責記者前日宣佈辭職，聲稱被迫撰寫錯誤報道而無法拒絕。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係香港就會變做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncctvb走狗： 我地打份工架渣 所有衰嘢都係袁花「迫」我地<br />\n智障左膠： 多謝你地係內部「守」住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗理班鬥黃撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5293c7c49fc1787fb25f72d019bec460d7a747b","tid":2510315,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"美國有保守派傳媒 東家唔打打世家"},{"pid":"8fd5714fddc796daafc039fd82695055923f95d5","tid":2510315,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:07:03.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敖狗幾時出句聲話記者係人渣法西斯？"},{"pid":"72dfcbfd97fbf2d0f0148e45d88539bc691b9bc5","tid":2510315,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8fd5714fddc796daafc039fd82695055923f95d5","tid":2510315,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:07:03.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hk